data.description: Beautiful Custom built Howell Home located in Palm Coast Plantation. A Prestigious Intracoastal gated community with lots of amenities. This 3,800 sqft living home with 5 bedrooms and 4.5 baths is nestled among beautiful matured landscaping, gorgeous oak trees, and a nature preserve on side and rear. Walk into this well designed custom home and enjoy the open floor plan with two master suites, mother in law suite and a gourmet kitchen to die for! Other upgrades include: 10ft ceilings on both floors, 8ft doors, can lighting/crown molding throughout, 42' raised maple cabinets w/crown molding, granite counter tops, surround sound, security system, two master jacuzzi tubs w/walk-in showers, and two private screened porches off the master bedrooms to enjoy the Florida Lifestyle. A must see!!
